
**popularly used in food it is dietery and nutritious it is whole some and suited to sick person the soup made of it is often the first article of diet prescribed recovery from actute illness it is said to be useful in relieving the heat and burning of the eyes when applied in the form of powder it removes the biliouness but adds vayo**
